## Section Red-Accent Titles (Figma pattern)
All section headings use a **split title** pattern where one word/phrase is colored red:
```jsx
<h2>
  {t("section.titlePrefix")}{" "}
  <span className="text-nihao-red-normal">{t("section.titleAccent")}</span>
</h2>
```

---

## Hero Brush Stroke
The "Chinese Language" highlight uses `.hero-brush` CSS class defined in `index.css`:
- Yellow/gold wavy underline via `::after` pseudo-element.
- Do NOT recreate this inline — always use the `.hero-brush` class on the `<span>`.

